                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=baxter",
                        "name": "baxter",
                        "displayName": "Jason Brumwell",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I agree, I am writing a cron portion of a site I'm working on and would like to use the original application config, which has:\n\nbootstrap.path = APPLICATION_PATH \"\/Bootstrap.php\"\nbootstrap.class = \"Bootstrap\"\n\nI would like to update that to my cron bootstrap.php file, through the option settings",
