                        "name": "sidhighwind",
                        "displayName": "Jon Whitcraft",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "After talking with Matthew about this issue it will not be made available in the 1.9.x cycle as it changes the behavior slightly.\r\n\r\nIt will be included in the 1.10 release.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=sidhighwind",
